snippet.title: Amber Heard - Johnny Depp Fight Analyzed by a Couples Therapist
snippet.description:
Dr. Kirk Honda analyzes the recorded fight between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. Was Johnny Depp a victim? Let's review the audio.
